────────────────────────────────────────

You are free to:

  Share — copy and redistribute the material in any medium or format
          for any purpose, even commercially.

The licensor cannot revoke these freedoms as long as you follow the
license terms.

Under the following terms:

  Attribution — You must give appropriate credit, provide a link to
                the license, and indicate if changes were made. You
                may do so in any reasonable manner, but not in any
                way that suggests the licensor endorses you or your
                use.

                For each Tianxunwen piece you redistribute, the
                full "source label" MUST be retained:

                    一天大人 太素天尊　天訊文 TX-YYYYMMDD-NNN
                    現示時間：YYYY年MM月DD日 HH:MM:SS

  NoDerivatives — If you remix, transform, or build upon the
                  material, you may not distribute the modified
                  material.

                  Specifically: the original Tianxunwen text MUST
                  NOT be paraphrased, abridged, or rewritten. Even
                  light editing of the original text is considered
                  a derivative and is NOT permitted.

  No additional restrictions — You may not apply legal terms or
                technological measures that legally restrict others
                from doing anything the license permits.

